Happy Birthday to the greatest fiancé anyone could dream of. To say you’ve made this past year a dream is such a woeful understatement. I’ve gotten to bear witness to so much of your brilliance. Your first book, you reaching new levels in your writing career, and so much more. Every day with you is such a gift, you always know how to make me laugh, and I can’t wait to spend the rest of my life with you. Thank you for being born and thank you for agreeing to go through life with me. ❤️

August 13th is a most auspicious day bc it is the day the two most important men in my life were born. Happy Birthday Dad! Thank you for always being there to push and inspire me, I’m so proud of the work you’re doing with NoHo Home-alliance and One LA. I couldn’t have asked for a better role model as a kid, or a better advocate as an adult. I love you so much.

Been having a lot of thoughts on the gaps between the lives and lifestyles of the influencers I follow here and on Tik Tok and my own- and how refreshing it would be to get cleaning advice from someone who struggles to maintain a steady cleaning schedule, recipes from someone who often comes home too tired to cook, etc. So I decided to launch a @substackinc where that is the exact content I put Into the world. Will I post regularly? I have no idea. Will I be able to keep this up? Also no idea. But click on the link in my bio to subscribe if you want to find out! And if nothing else I’ll always have this adorable logo I made in @canva.
I guess I’m hard launching my substack on Instagram? First reel, first blog.
